od at his dormitory, he accidentally gets connected to the Goddess Hotline and a beautiful goddess named Belldandy appears out of a mirror in front of him. After getting kicked out of the dorm, Keiichi and Belldandy move to an old shrine and soon afterwards, Belldandy\'s sisters Urd and Skuld move in.', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff'),
