he jungle with his father, Kenjurou. By a twist of fate, the determined samurai, Yaiba, returns to Japan and encounters his rival, Onimaru Takeshi. Yaiba, who lives for serious battles, embarks on a spectacular adventure when Onimaru obtains the \"Legendary Demon Sword!\" \n\n(Source: Shogakukan, edited)', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff'),
