gings after he passed away. And a boy\'s mother tells him that his father had been a gardener in the past. Then he figures out the scissors were made by Sasuke, who is an artisan living in a foreign country. The boy travels all the way to a place where Sasuke lives in order to get his scissors fixed.\n\n(Source: Official site)', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff'),
