en she meets Kamegawa, her new Kouhai. He\'s cute, a little nerdy, and easy to talk to. How will this awkward Senpai be able to handle these new feelings?!\n\n(Source: Comikey Media)', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff'),
