e first outposts in the far reaches of space is WATCHER\'S NEST - an inflation hole drive portal - which has recently come under attack by a mysterious force known simply as GHOUL... A group of young female cadets assigned to the portal are unexpectedly thrown into a hornet\'s nest of trouble as they finalize their training to become an elite pilot in the Seraphim Squadron.\n\n(Source: DVD Collection Back Cover)', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff'),
