rld Series. However, after an unexpected accident during the match with his fated rival, his quest in becoming the world\'s best becomes more challenging. Undaunted, Gorou continues to put the weight of his dreams into every pitch he makes, and forges a path towards his desired future through high-speed pitching.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]', '#252525', '#333333', '#ffffff', '#ffffff', '#ffffff');
